<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
	<meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8" />
	<title>{{.Username}}, please verify your e-mail address</title>
</head>

<body>
	<p>Ola <b>{{.Username}}</b>,</p>
	<p>Por favor fai click na seguinte ligazón para verificar a túa conta de correo electrónico en <b>{{.ActiveCodeLives}} hours</b>:</p>
	<p><a href="{{AppUrl}}user/activate_email?code={{.Code}}&email={{.Email}}">{{AppUrl}}user/activate_email?code={{.Code}}&email={{.Email}}</a></p>
	<p>Non funciona? Proba a copiar e pegar no teu navegador de internet.</p>
	<p><a target="_blank" href="{{AppUrl}}">{{AppName}}</a></p>
</body>
</html>
